      </div>

      <div class="partner-stat">
        <div class="partner-stat__figure">100%</div>
        <div class="partner-stat__label">documented survival</div>
        <p>Across 401 cases of exertional heat stroke treated with immediate cold water immersion, survival rate is 100% when core temperature drops below 40°C within 30 minutes. This is the global clinical reference standard. Source: Dr Douglas Casa, Korey Stringer Institute, UConn.</p>
